snippet.title: DAWNMAKER - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Dawnmaker is a turn-based colony builder and resource management game. Create powerful combinations between your buildings and cards, rekindle the old lighthouses and bring life back to the lost continent.

Wishlist now: https://s.team/a/2749100

And follow us on:
▶️ Twitter: https://twitter.com/ArpentorStudio
▶️ Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Arpentor-Studio-100396392569735
▶️ Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/arpentorstudio/

Sound by Pierre-François Renouf and music by Nicolas Cornil, from Studio Le Refuge - https://www.studiolerefuge.fr/
